Classes in Seduction is a great hentai DVD, but only one episode and I wish they make some more episodes. This is about a hot and sexy Professor at a local school where some bullies harass other students for money and breaking rules, and a horny, but shy schoolgirl who wants a lesson about sex. I gave this DVD 5 stars.

This feature has decent animation, with a bit too much 'pan and scan' of still shots or backgrounds (an obvious attempt at cutting costs). As for the story, well, it's an adult-themed cartoon, 'Gone with the Wind' it's not. A female professor, who doesn't look much older than her students, helps several of them discover their budding sexuality. The best scene involves a cute girl and the handsome baseball player she has a crush on. Both are virgins. The comely professor gently but erotically guides them through their first intimate encounter. Another sequence involves the teacher being ravished by three 'tough' guys, which more closely resembles a gang rape. But did the guys really have their way with her, or did she have HER way with them?? You'll have to decide for yourself. Some of the so-called 'outtakes' are actually pretty funny.
